{"tid":1857302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上海同事話佢捐出去嘅物資係淘寶買得返......","createTime":"2020-02-02T06:28:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T13:04:07.000Z","uid":28938,"like":778,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"5862d024b035d5f1f0e57690e3b838838666401d","tid":1857302,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T06:28:29.000Z","msg":"上海同事話捐咗啲外國口罩俾武漢紅十字會，轉過頭就係淘寶搵到，幅相仲要係同微信溝通果時俾個組織staff 嘅相一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我本來都半信半疑，跟住有重慶同事俾咗呢堆笑話我睇，我睇到第四個就笑咗了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yARX9gx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyARX9gx.jpg&h=b0f087bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支共有武漢紅十<br />\n香港有國難五金<br />\n<br />\n兩班人都係食人血饅頭嘅仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"617e746d12607acf05587a08d09e3e344115dd18","tid":1857302,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T06:40:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b5026e337706260a26f5d27b99f9b439d8d6e5c","tid":1857302,"uid":41545,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T06:47:14.000Z","msg":"中國紅十字會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"700ca37be25b72cbc83f6c1f0e0aa68d7e7bc918","tid":1857302,"uid":52946,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T06:52:59.000Z","msg":"紅十字呢期真係賺撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ddaaeb774b5b96804bc08cc2279b83831f1e85","tid":1857302,"uid":29879,"like":88,"dislike":4,"score":84,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T07:09:26.000Z","msg":"睇完個post上淘寶睇下， 十間有8間賣緊救救口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}